{"tid":1474631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子九龍灣連儂牆傷人　獲控方撤控","createTime":"2019-08-15T08:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:17:17.000Z","uid":106870,"like":9,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e6bac47fcf7a5c6fba3ba582f3c7179dbeb103","tid":1474631,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名男子因連儂牆問題與人爭執，踢傷另一人，被控普通襲擊提堂，獲控方撤控。<br />\n<br />\n63歲被告梁炳全在觀塘裁判法院提堂。他承認上月11日在九龍灣巴士站附近踢傷一名男子腹部，控方決定不提起訴，他准以1000元自簽守行為12個月及繳付500元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n事發時被告企圖阻止一名男子撕毀連儂牆的貼紙，雙方因而發生衝突，由路人報警，被告稱衝動下踢傷對方。<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=359262&amp;refer=Share&amp;fbclid=IwAR3j-rG1zLDzZXwLAKa3P1sioaugdCp3oTxPi5DCuNiWsvO_Pa-3haXNogk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359262%26refer%3DShare%26fbclid%3DIwAR3j-rG1zLDzZXwLAKa3P1sioaugdCp3oTxPi5DCuNiWsvO_Pa-3haXNogk&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXduIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=5712dc93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359262%26refer%3DShare%26fbclid%3DIwAR3j-rG1zLDzZXwLAKa3P1sioaugdCp3oTxPi5DCuNiWsvO_Pa-3haXNogk&h=d7d632b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=359262&amp;refer=Share&amp;fbclid=IwAR3j-rG1zLDzZXwLAKa3P1sioaugdCp3oTxPi5DCuNiWsvO_Pa-3haXNogk</a>"},{"pid":"ea003c12dca36bcf55e5fdbe910c80761f438bca","tid":1474631,"uid":265959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ead2748e4f2b37624f422abe5028ebbe5720dcd","tid":1474631,"uid":281904,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:51:41.000Z","msg":"睇清楚，係義士獲撤控，唔係打人十幾拳果條藍屍"},{"pid":"eb680214871b648e6120ae552787acdc93fc7091","tid":1474631,"uid":24558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"嘩 痴線<img src=\"/